file.name: merge-keys-with-duplicate-props.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0

x-format-version: "1.0"

info:
  title: Merge key issue
  description: https://yaml.org/type/merge.html
  version: 1.0.0

x-center: &CENTER
  x: 1
  y: 2

x-left: &LEFT
  x: 0
  y: 2

x-big: &BIG
  r: 10

x-small: &SMALL
  r: 1

x-one:
  <<: *CENTER
  r: 10
  label: center/big
x-two:
  <<: [*CENTER, *BIG]
  label: center/big
x-three:
  <<: [*BIG, *LEFT, *SMALL]
  x: 1
  label: center/big

paths: {}
